Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A stranger's not allowed \Nto save this country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eight days before the great battle...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Luffy and the others had conquered Udon\Nunbeknownst to the enemy's main army.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Warriors' Dream!\NLuffy's Conquer of Udon!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're free!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defeat Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, hurrah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, hurrah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, hurrah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys can't back down anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna fight Kaido again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look what happened to my buddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank me for not killing \Nyou right here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sick of forming alliances.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't believe anyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To take back our crewmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go our own way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look what 20 years can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is very hard to keep \Nbelieving in a hopeful dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They could not wait more than 10 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They became impatient\Nand went to Onigashima...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they all died!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been 10 years!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:47.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,10 YEARS AGO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've grown so old.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we wait for 20 years,\Nwe'll get even weaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you asking us to wait for those people\Nwhose return isn't guaranteed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in Toki-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s words...\NBelieve in them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin'emon will come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with Momonosuke-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have nothing to eat\Nsince we don't submit ourselves to Orochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disease will kill us before a fight does!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kaido's army!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you destroy the well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't take it anymore, Shutenmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go and take down Kaido...\Nand Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna just grow old\Nand die without doing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Your death will be senseless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no chance unless you form a big army\Nunder Kozuki's banner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us at least die holding our swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we die, we wanna die as samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let us go!\N--Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You men, calm down!\NRisking your lives now will not change a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not cowards like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll choose how we die ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let us go!\N--Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us have our revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that you've borne will have been in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go now, you cannot avenge Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember? When we were kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We used to shout out that word\Nand test our courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, placing too much value on yourself\Nmakes people cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunacchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Su{\i0}-rrender your {\i1}na{\i0}-me and be as a {\i1}chi{\i0}-ld.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the leap without thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the word means!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your voice! Sunacchi!
