Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it have to take 20 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will know once this is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be a meaning to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no reason to distrust Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight days from now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the night of the Fire Festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the name of Kozuki,\Nwe will raid Onigashima...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to take the pirate Kaido\Nand the Shogun Orochi's heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those of you who are determined,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we will, Chief!\NWe've been waiting for this day for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have not changed \Nsince that day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were the same age at that time, but now that\Nwe've lived 20 years longer, we are stronger than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, doggie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you old farts! \NDo not get in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You squirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa-whoa, stop!\NNo one can stop a fight among the Akazaya members!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:32.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,UDON
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The straw hat guy is a pirate\Njust like Kaido?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he is, but he is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't trust him!\NWe know he'll betray us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all people, why did you bring a pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the world is big\Nand there are many different kinds of pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man is crucial for \Nus to bring down Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How can we trust him?!\N--We need a good explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, no. We are missing something.\NThey came to their senses, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, is it true\Nthat you came from 20 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raizo-{\i1}san{\i0}, you always looked \Nolder than your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we can't tell\Nif you've actually aged 20 years or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might not mean to,\Nbut you are hurting my feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the straw hat man go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama, you shouldn't have come this far.\NIt's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Big Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad that you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He is barely alive.\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro, show some guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find an antibody soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have pretended\Nthat it wouldn't affect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be painful!\NWhy didn't you think it through?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say sorry to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We thank them! But now that we know they're pirates,\Nwe won't join with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Then we can't take down Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw hat man is trustworthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are all the same to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy may be stupid but he is quite special.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could not have done something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momo, you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a real idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and a coward...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and a weakling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and a wimp...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You are so rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no business talking to me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momo-{\i1}kun{\i0}, don't hit him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, a chicken?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kozuki Momonosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kozuki Oden's son!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then go, Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't trust pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop, you fool!\NAre you going to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think they're waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, yeah...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What we were missing was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a dream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What lies ahead of this battle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is not me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think what everyone is seeing\Nis my father...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The great shadow of Kozuki\Nthat protected the Land of Wano!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I cannot do it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I cannot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to bring down Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Momonosuke!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do not be afraid, Momonosuke...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do not be afraid, Momonosuke!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everyone, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened at Oden Castle that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:21:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went on a journey searching for allies\Nalong with Kin'emon and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I strayed from them\Nand was floundering about helplessly in a dangerous place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could not come back without the help of\NLuffy and the others who I met along the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not strong enough yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I will avenge everyone at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even through difficult times,\NI could carry on without giving up...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because of one wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To realize that, I need like-minded allies...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.62,0:21:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need the help of you all\Nwho are living in the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all share one wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take back the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone... For the last 20 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:22:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thank you for waiting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.14,0:22:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the heir to the Daimyo \Nof the Land of the Wano...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kozuki Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time to rise up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am relieved to know that\NMomonosuke-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s grown up strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is some place I urgently need to go.\NI promise I will join you all before the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.56,0:22:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. See you then!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.21,0:23:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Orochi has a plan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.30,0:23:23.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Shogun's scheme drives \Nthe Straw Hats into a corner
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:27.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and destroys the plot to \Ntake back the Land of Wano!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But to counteract this, Zorojuro, the swordsman, rises up!\NHe will punish the vice-ridden world!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Orochi's Hunting Party! The Ninja Group vs. Zoro!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.03,0:23:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
